subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: The defending champion Jelena Jankovic and the French Open runner-up Dinara Safina will not compete at the DFS Classic in Birmingham, England, which starts Monday. Jankovic withdrew from the event, a Wimbledon warm-up, with an arm injury, which caused her to fly home to Serbia after losing in the French semifinals. Safina withdrew with a bad back.
